Behind the scenes, Pence has kept a close eye on nearly every internal function linked to the administration’s Covid-19 response.
He consults with White House senior adviser and Trump son-in-law Jared Kushner several times each day, monitoring his efforts to partner with private sector companies and address supply chain issues across the country.
That is the central nervous system of this effort; the president made it that way,” said White House counselor Kellyanne Conway.
In just about every case, the vice president stood by silently as the president carried on.
